title.$t: The 2nd Annual Paul F. Tompkins Memorial Moustache Formal and Feztravaganza

content.$t: Paul F. Tompkins hosts this fancy, fancy event for fancy, fancy people and their moustaches and fezzes. Formal wear, moustaches, and fezzes optional; moustaches provided upon request.

This is your chance to shine. Sing, dance, play, tell jokes, emote...come on out and show us what you've got. Guaranteed to be a 100% safe, supportive environment. (In other words, no jerks allowed) Please keep all performances to 5 minutes or less.
Paul and Storm record a live version of their podcast, "Paul and Storm Talk About Some Stuff for Five to Ten Minutes (On Average)". Guests TBD.
